    "description": "Worldseekers 是一款 GPS 探索类 RPG。在深入探索这个世界广阔的土地和迷宫时，您可以发现稀有的卡牌、事件和独特的角色。<br><br>为了帮助 <strong>促进身心健康</strong>，Worldseekers 使用 GPS 机制并链接到手机应用程序，帮助您外出散步。当然，Steam 版本允许您在 PC 上玩几个小时，同时仍会奖励您多散步一次。对于所有主播，我们默认调整/隐藏位置。<br><br>也可以注册我们的电子邮件简报：（我们仍然有所有其他社交媒体内容，但在我看来电子邮件更好）<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >将世界变成一个充满神秘和奥秘的奇幻之地：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>击败独特而难对付的怪物<br></li><li>享受有趣和令人费解的叙述<br></li><li>不断变化的土地适应您的游戏风格<br></li><li>将地牢和其他内容带回家，以奖励自己养成健康的习惯</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索一个充满神秘和魔法的广阔世界。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031060/extras/730721d22cf84bb4d5e4ac64ee6b0f12.poster.avif?t=1766557985\" width=182 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031060/extras/730721d22cf84bb4d5e4ac64ee6b0f12.webm?t=1766557985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031060/extras/730721d22cf84bb4d5e4ac64ee6b0f12.mp4?t=1766557985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与传奇生物战斗并探索地牢深度。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031060/extras/c30a8d4dd88ec6bb71589b72bf6960d3.poster.avif?t=1766557985\" width=172 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031060/extras/c30a8d4dd88ec6bb71589b72bf6960d3.webm?t=1766557985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031060/extras/c30a8d4dd88ec6bb71589b72bf6960d3.mp4?t=1766557985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与众多城镇居民建立关系。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031060/extras/60f982604300f6895b50078ec1320710.poster.avif?t=1766557985\" width=170 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031060/extras/60f982604300f6895b50078ec1320710.webm?t=1766557985\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031060/extras/60f982604300f6895b50078ec1320710.mp4?t=1766557985\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果您有疑问、反馈或想要支持我们（我们肯定会使用它），请随时在 Twitch 或 YouTube 上与我联系（最终 Boss 编辑）！",
